11<br>12<br>13<br>14<br>15<br>16<br>17<br>18<br>19<br>20<br>21<br>22","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":5,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"module","slug":"module","count":1,"path":"api/tags/module.json"}]},{"title":"config-kernel-arm","slug":"config-kernel-arm","date":"2019-11-13T02:34:34.000Z","updated":"2019-11-20T13:38:47.955Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/config-kernel-arm.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"linux-内核的配置\"><a href=\"#linux-内核的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux 内核的配置\"></a><code>linux</code> 内核的配置</h1>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg","content":null,"text":"linux 内核的配置四种打开方式make configmake menuconfigmake xconfigmake gconfigmenuconfig 如下所示 [Figure] ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":5,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"},{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":5,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"}]},{"title":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","slug":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","date":"2019-11-13T01:54:56.000Z","updated":"2019-11-18T11:25:20.686Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/build-linux-kenel-in-qumu.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\"><a href=\"#在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\"></a>在<code>QEMU</code>中运行编译的<code>Linux</code>内核</h1>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg","content":null,"text":"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核内核编译脚本 build.sh1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>export ARCH=arm<br>export EXTRADIR=$&#123;PWD&#125;/extr","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":5,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"},{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":5,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"}]},{"title":"funds","slug":"funds","date":"2019-03-29T15:17:18.000Z","updated":"2019-11-18T11:25:21.004Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/funds.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"从零开始的基金之路\"><a href=\"#从零开始的基金之路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"从零开始的基金之路\"></a>从零开始的基金之路</h1><p>人生有哲学，而哲学是指导思考的元科学。同样的，基金的操作也<br>应该有思考反思遵循的哲学。</p>\n<h2 id=\"根本准则-：-追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\"><a href=\"#根本准则-：-追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"根本准则 ： 追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\"></a>根本准则 ： <code>追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格</code></h2><p>若总的持有价格小于当前，且这个差值的累积之和，那么就可以使得<br>基金增持。</p>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"从零开始的基金之路人生有哲学，而哲学是指导思考的元科学。同样的，基金的操作也<br>应该有思考反思遵循的哲学。根本准则 ： 追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格若总的持有价格小于当前，且这个差值的累积之和，那么就可以使得<br>基金增持。此路缘何当作养成游戏的娱乐养成储蓄的习惯保持学","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"基金","slug":"基金","count":1,"path":"api/tags/基金.json"}]}]}